# ===== General Patterns =====

# Common false positives in blockchain/crypto projects:
# Contract addresses (these are public)
0x[a-fA-F0-9]{40}

# Test private keys (these are for testing only)
test/fixtures/**
*.test.*

# Documentation examples (contains fake secrets for illustration)
docs/**/*.md
README.md

# Environment example files
.env.example
*.env.example

# Package lock files may contain hashes that look like secrets
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
poetry.lock

# Build artifacts and temporary files
dist/
build/
node_modules/
.nyc_output/
coverage/
